highlights.text: “Came Here for Love” by Sigala and Ella Eyre is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 81 spots at #115.
Lorde has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Green Light” is the highest at #67.
“Wild Thoughts (feat. Rihanna & Bryson Tiller)” by DJ Khaled, Rihanna, and Bryson Tiller is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #5.
“That's What I Like” by Bruno Mars has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 26 weeks straight.
